# D9: keep the Docker build context small and reproducible — exclude build output, VCS, IDE files,
# the separately-built frontend/mock, docs, and local run artifacts. The Java service Dockerfiles
# COPY the repo root, so anything not needed to run `mvn package` should be excluded here.
**/target/
.git/
.gitattributes
.gitignore

**/node_modules/
**/dist/
frontend/
mock/

*.log
scripts/load/*.txt

.idea/
*.iml
*.iws
.vscode/
.settings/
.classpath
.project

.env
*.md
docs/
